metadata.name: Chilled Ape #1
metadata.description: Chilled Apes is a community driven collection of 2000 stylistically curated NFTs chilling on the Ethereum blockchain. Much like humans, no two apes are alike,  each 1-of-1 Chilled Ape comes in a joyful range of colors and traits. Some apes rarer than others, created from tens of millions of possible combinations with traits like breed, body, mouth, eyes & more. Visit [chilledapes.io](https://chilledapes.io) for more details.
